race.description: Flinders Island Cabin Park Hidden Zebra Mdn Plt
race.comment: CELESTIAL GLOW (4) drew out and didn't have the best of it first up and will be better for it. She's been desperately unlucky not to have broken through and she's likely to position forward today. Goes close with the extra fitness. SKY OF GOLD (6) raced in tougher grade on debut and then resumed here against the above and found one much too good. Covered the others and can build quickly on that. Maps well and the 2kg claim is handy. TIMELY NEEDS (2) raced wide on debut in the same contest well in the betting. Presents fitter as well and the top hoop takes over today replacing the apprentice. The winkers go on and expect a much better effort. Stablemate CAN'T CATCH CHILLI (3) proved difficult to load first up and looked short of a run. She's trialled okay since as required and fitter won't be far away drawn to advantage.
